<h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333; text-align: center;">New Request Notification</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Dear <%= agentName %>,</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Thank you for submitting a new request for a <strong><%= requestType %></strong>.</p>
<p style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Request Details:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
<ul style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #333333; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li><strong>Request ID:</strong>"<%= request_id %>"</li>
    <li><strong>Request Type:</strong>"<%= requestType %>"</li>
</ul>
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">You can view the full request details below:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/requests/permissions/<%= request_id %>" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: #0056b3; border-radius: 5px;">
        View Request Details
    </a>
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">A supervisor from the team is going to review your request shortly. You will be notified of its status once the review is completed.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Best regards, <br>
    The support team
</p>
